# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:2
translate portuguese u20f_7d92946f:

    # "For now, I should go see Mari."
    "Por agora, tenho de ir ver a Mari."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:5
translate portuguese u20f_2bb3b023:

    # "I drive to Mari's house and knock on her door."
    "Dirijo-me à casa da Mari e bato à porta."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:6
translate portuguese u20f_0b175aad:

    # "Her dogs start barking at the door and I hear footsteps approaching."
    "Os cães dela começam a ladrar à porta e ouço passos a aproximarem-se."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:7
translate portuguese u20f_be91a4c9:

    # fr "Who is it?"
    fr "Quem é?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:8
translate portuguese u20f_1063bb8b:

    # pc "It's me! [pcname]."
    pc "Sou eu! [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:12
translate portuguese u20f_a9b3d399:

    # fr "Oh my God, [pcname]!"
    fr "Meu Deus, [pcname]!"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:13
translate portuguese u20f_ea03fec2:

    # "She opens the door and stares at me for a moment, shocked."
    "Ela abre a porta e fica a olhar para mim por um momento, chocada."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:14
translate portuguese u20f_40412d0f:

    # "I can see her eyes welling up with tears."
    "Vejo os seus olhos a encherem-se de lágrimas."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:15
translate portuguese u20f_23647146:

    # fr "I thought..."
    fr "Pensei que..."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:18
translate portuguese u20f_540e25ed:

    # "She rushes into my arms and hugs me tightly."
    "Ela corre para os meus braços e abraça-me com força."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:19
translate portuguese u20f_140e4956:

    # "I hug her back, feeling her warmth and the softness of her body."
    "Abraço-a de volta, sentindo o seu calor e a suavidade do seu corpo."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:20
translate portuguese u20f_dddaeb84:

    # pc "I missed you, Mari. I'm sorry I was gone for so long."
    pc "Tive saudades tuas, Mari. Desculpa ter estado fora tanto tempo."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:23
translate portuguese u20f_b77230d2:

    # fr "I was so worried about you. I thought that machine killed you."
    fr "Estava tão preocupado contigo. Pensei que aquela máquina te tivesse matado."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:24
translate portuguese u20f_40e4fe9b:

    # pc "I fought so hard to get back."
    pc "Lutei tanto para voltar."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:25
translate portuguese u20f_356f7f42:

    # pc "I'll tell you everything tomorrow, I promise."
    pc "Conto-te tudo amanhã, prometo."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:28
translate portuguese u20f_e5e85df6:

    # fr "I'm just glad you're back."
    fr "Só estou feliz por estares de volta."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:29
translate portuguese u20f_1f943087:

    # fr "Wow, your hair grew a lot."
    fr "Uau, o teu cabelo cresceu imenso."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:30
translate portuguese u20f_c49af8d0:

    # fr "It makes you look all rugged."
    fr "Dá-te um ar tão rude."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:33
translate portuguese u20f_7d64063d:

    # "She kisses me softly, her lips warm and inviting."
    "Ela beija-me suavemente, os seus lábios quentes e convidativos."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:34
translate portuguese u20f_e6ca1864:

    # fr "I'm so happy you came home."
    fr "Estou tão feliz por teres voltado para casa."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20f.rpy:35
translate portuguese u20f_402e55b1:

    # fr "Let's go to bed. We can talk in the morning."
    fr "Vamos para a cama. Podemos conversar de manhã."

